 to intermodulation distortion are placed away from the\nsensitive region in the TES response and the X-ray performance is consistent\nwith the single-pixel, on-resonance level.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 16:19:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-04"}
