he\nstellar multiple systems, but their properties drastically change with a tiny\namount of metals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 23:29:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2021 11:12:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 14:31:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
