 photo-centre. However, this contribution would be restricted to this\nlocation only, double scattering process being the most important contributor\nto polarisation in the equatorial plane of the AGN and single scattering being\ndominant in the polar outflow bi-cone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2021 03:34:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-14"}
