antageous, eliminating direct H-loss as a\ncompeting process. The observed loss of primarily [2C,2H] can be explained\nthrough entropy calculations that show favored loss of [2C,2H] at higher\ninternal energies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2021 09:52:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-15"}
