in\nall three $\\widehat{T}{}^{(s)}_n[f]$ are $O(e^{-2n\\pi\\sigma/T})$ as\n$n\\to\\infty$, for all practical purposes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2021 12:06:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-15"}
